&lt;li&gt;Ensure data governance practices are aligned and upheld within the Decision Intelligence teams strategic framework.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide training and support to end users to enhance data literacy and ensure effective use of BI tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
