&lt;li&gt;Inspect formed cases, shrink wrapped cases, labeled bottles, and bottles placed in carriers, verifying and adjusting the process and equipment to meet finished goods specifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stop or reset machines when malfunctions occur, clear machine jams, and report malfunctions to a supervisor.&lt;/li&gt;
