&lt;li&gt;Review product and equipment specifications to ensure conformance to product specifications are realized&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review all nonconforming product or ingredients with Quality Assurance Manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor processing department throughout shift and&amp;nbsp;assure&amp;nbsp;employee compliance with GMP’s, sanitation, and safety. Review daily audit reports&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Verify that all plant processing equipment is in good working condition and all preventative maintenance is being performed on a scheduled basis by reviewing Preventive Maintenance schedules with the Maintenance Manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
